Bundled payload
---------------

This repository includes bundled files used by the 3D HUD VPK Merger.

- Compiled 3D HUD payload files in public/payload/3d-hud/ are generated from
  Hantu-Raya/Deadlock-mods-collection main/3d hud source so the browser tool
  can merge them into an uploaded Deadlock addon VPK.
- panorama/scripts/3d_hero_dynamic.js is minified with Terser before the
  Source 2 compiler wrapper emits panorama/scripts/3d_hero_dynamic.vjs_c.
- panorama/layout/hud_health_container.vxml_c is preserved as a compiled
  compatibility payload file because the current upstream raw 3D HUD source
  does not include a matching layout XML file.
- Deadlock and Source 2 names, paths, and file formats belong to their
  respective owners. This is an unofficial fan-made tool and is not affiliated
  with Valve.

Runtime and libraries
---------------------

- Astro, React, Playwright, Terser, and npm dependencies: see each package's
  license in package-lock.json and upstream repositories.
- The local Source 2 compiler helper expects user-provided Deadlock mod source
  and compiler paths at runtime. The helper does not upload VPKs to a server.

Generated artifacts
-------------------

The repository should not commit Astro build output. Regenerate it with
npm run build when needed. Regenerate the bundled 3D HUD payload with
npm run payload:sync when upstream 3d hud source changes.
